==Bosnian==
===Idiom===
'''mirna Bosna'''
# literally: ''peaceful Bosnia''
# an outcome of an event in which all parties involved are satisfied
#: ''Podijelićemo pare jednako i '''mirna Bosna'''.'' (We will split the money equally and everybody will be happy.)
